<template>
  <VueMultiselect :options="cities" selected></VueMultiselect>
</template>
<script>

import axios from "axios";
import VueMultiselect from 'vue-multiselect'
export default {
  name: "AgendaPage",
  components : {
    VueMultiselect
  },
  data(){
    return{
      email_professore : "pippo@gmail.com",
      titolo_corso : 'Matematica',
      mydata : null,
      selected : null,
      cities : [
        {id : 1,name : 'Asti'},
        {id : 2,name : 'Torino'},
        {id : 3,name : 'Milano'},
      ]
    }
  },
  methods : {
    async Foo(){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletGetAvBookings',{params : {emailProfessore : this.email_professore,titoloCorso : this.titolo_corso}})
        this.mydata = response.data
      }catch (e){
        console.log(e)
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style>
  .spacer{
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
</style>
